snippet.title: Titan Warriors (NES - Unreleased) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A complete playthrough of Capcom's unreleased 1988 NES prototype game, Titan Warriors. This game was intended to be the Famicom sequel to the arcade game Vulgus.
_______
No cheats were used during the recording of this video. 

NintendoComplete (http://www.nintendocomplete.com/) punches you in the face with in-depth reviews, screenshot archives, and music from classic 8-bit NES games!
